---
That's a sad sight. Maybe you can repair it.
<<if getWood() >= 10 and getStones() >= 10>>
	Use your 10 wood logs and stones?
	-> Repair
		<<addWood -10>>
		<<addStones -10>>
		<<action repairWell>>
		<<progress wellRepaired true>>
		Tada! All fixed up!
	-> Ignore
		<<stop>>
<<else>>
	You'll need 10 wood logs and 10 stones.
<<endif>>
